## Cursor-Specific Tips

- Use Cursor's "Composer" for multi-file edits (respects ADR-003 ports)
- Use "Code Search" to find where ports are imported
- Enable "Test Explorer" to track TDD progress
- Use "Documentation Generator" to add decision comments

